## C. Hooks for software / this repo

| Idea | Engineering use |
|------|-------------------|
| **Resulting** | A green deploy after a sloppy change is still luck; don’t drop standards. |
| **Base rate / outside view** | Reference class: “How did similar refactors or migrations go?” before estimates. |
| **Premortem / 10-10-10** | Plan *Risks*, rollback, and “what fails first” before merge. |
| **WYSIATI** | If the plan feels complete, list **what’s not on the page**. |
| **RPV (Christensen)** | New processes need **new** habits/automation — not only more people. |
| **Discovery-driven** | Smallest experiment that falsifies the riskiest assumption (feature flags, canary). |
| **Barbell** | Core stability (main, `ship:gate`) + small bounded bets (experiments), not mushy middle risk. |

